body:
@cbaenziger Since the test environment is complicated to set up and the test time is long, we use pulse for internal CI(Jenkins CI with github plugin triggered by each commit is only used for simple building test). But we only built centos/redhat linux distribution cluster for build and feature/perf test.

We can merge your pull request immediately(after your rebase) and if the pulse CI do not pass, I will send further pull request and AT you to discuss.

Advice: since hawq is a apache project, you must follow the apache standard to contribute. Specifically, please rebase your commits into one or two commits with obvious meaning. Each commit info must starts with "HAWQ-307. ".
